high_descs: Turn around, walk to the end, turn left, walk to the shelf
Grab the green sponge from the blue trash bin
Turn around, walk to the toilet
Put the sponge by the paper roll on the toilet
anns.task_desc: Move the green sponge from the blue trash bin to the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight until you reach the wall. Then turn left and walk to the metal rack and the blue bin.
Pick up the green sponge from the blue bin.
Turn around and walk straight to toilet.
Put the sponge on the water tank of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put the green sponge from the blue bin on top of the water tank of the toilet.

high_descs: Move to the blue trash bin that is to the right of the silver shelves
Pick up the green sponge that is inside of the trash can
Carry the green sponge to the toilet
Place the sponge on the back of the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: Move a sponge from the trash to the back of the toilet
